WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 10=

00:00:30.140 --> 00:00:31.580
Your...

00:00:32.580 --> 00:00:34.260
Your leg...

00:00:35.340 --> 00:00:36.940
After being crippled for three years,

00:00:37.340 --> 00:00:39.700
I can finally stand again today.

00:00:39.940 --> 00:00:41.259
Mother,

00:00:41.260 --> 00:00:43.540
I truly have you to thank for this.

00:00:45.820 --> 00:00:48.139
I've remembered every "gift"

00:00:48.140 --> 00:00:49.940
you gave me over these past three years.

00:00:50.660 --> 00:00:52.820
From now on,

00:00:54.740 --> 00:00:58.260
I'll repay them all in full.

00:00:58.700 --> 00:01:01.740
And if anyone dares
lay a hand on my daughter again,

00:01:02.860 --> 00:01:05.660
they'd better think twice first.

00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:10.939
Suisui, let's go.

00:01:10.940 --> 00:01:12.380
Wait, Father.

00:01:12.500 --> 00:01:14.460
I need to grab something first.

00:01:23.500 --> 00:01:26.140
No reason to waste
the emotional damage compensation.

00:01:41.220 --> 00:01:44.300
And we can't waste all this food either.
We'll take it back for an extra meal.

00:01:44.820 --> 00:01:45.940
Let's go.

00:01:54.330 --> 00:01:55.169
I'm furious!

00:01:55.170 --> 00:01:55.979
I'm furious!

00:01:55.980 --> 00:01:58.240
I'm so furious!

00:02:00.100 --> 00:02:01.620
Your Highness...

00:02:01.660 --> 00:02:03.180
Don't touch me!

00:02:07.660 --> 00:02:09.100
Suisui,

00:02:10.100 --> 00:02:11.220
thank you.

00:02:11.380 --> 00:02:13.780
Why are you thanking me?

00:02:13.940 --> 00:02:15.520
I never thought

00:02:16.200 --> 00:02:18.300
I'd be able to stand again
in this lifetime.

00:02:19.500 --> 00:02:21.580
Thank you for healing my leg.

00:02:21.620 --> 00:02:23.659
No need to be so polite with me.

00:02:23.660 --> 00:02:26.179
But Father, why does

00:02:26.180 --> 00:02:27.779
Consort Shu want to hurt you?

00:02:27.780 --> 00:02:30.260
Isn't she your real mother?

00:02:32.740 --> 00:02:35.980
In her heart, there's only Xiao Jing.

00:02:37.340 --> 00:02:40.140
I used to think
I just wasn't good enough.

00:02:41.060 --> 00:02:42.580
I fought desperately to earn merit,

00:02:43.220 --> 00:02:45.620
hoping she'd look at me
just one more time.

00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:48.960
Three years ago, during the battle
at the northern border,

00:02:49.660 --> 00:02:54.140
out of thirty thousand soldiers,
I was the only one who returned alive.

00:02:55.380 --> 00:02:56.780
The day I came back to the capital,

00:02:57.180 --> 00:03:00.140
everyone in the streets
called me useless,

00:03:01.220 --> 00:03:02.340
a jinx.

00:03:03.780 --> 00:03:05.580
Then Mother came.

00:03:07.940 --> 00:03:10.300
She slapped me across the face

00:03:10.820 --> 00:03:13.220
and called me a cursed lone star,

00:03:14.580 --> 00:03:16.240
one who brings ruin
to the family and lord.

00:03:18.060 --> 00:03:19.900
Father, listen to me.

00:03:19.940 --> 00:03:22.059
Those people are blind idiots.

00:03:22.060 --> 00:03:24.019
You're not a jinx at all.

00:03:24.020 --> 00:03:25.660
You're my father.

00:03:28.060 --> 00:03:29.139
As long as I'm here,

00:03:29.140 --> 00:03:30.579
no one gets to bully you.

00:03:30.580 --> 00:03:32.300
Not even the King of Heaven himself.

00:03:32.660 --> 00:03:33.820
Good.

00:03:33.900 --> 00:03:35.419
That's more like it.

00:03:35.420 --> 00:03:38.419
From now on, Father, just stick with me.

00:03:38.420 --> 00:03:40.100
You'll live well and eat well.

00:03:41.500 --> 00:03:42.499
But Father,

00:03:42.500 --> 00:03:43.699
those poisonous bugs today

00:03:43.700 --> 00:03:45.660
weren't ordinary insects.

00:03:46.180 --> 00:03:49.500
Whoever raised them
must have powerful backing.

00:03:50.220 --> 00:03:51.739
The Imperial Preceptor, Wu Wang.

00:03:51.740 --> 00:03:54.379
The one who read my fate back then

00:03:54.380 --> 00:03:55.659
was him.

00:03:55.660 --> 00:03:57.139
Read your fate?

00:03:57.140 --> 00:03:59.980
Who does he think he is?

00:04:00.300 --> 00:04:02.379
Father, listen to me.

00:04:02.380 --> 00:04:05.340
The only one who can decide
your fate is Heaven.

00:04:05.420 --> 00:04:09.579
And Heaven is my grandpa.

00:04:09.580 --> 00:04:11.620
So don't worry, Father.

00:04:11.740 --> 00:04:13.099
As long as I'm here,

00:04:13.100 --> 00:04:14.780
you have nothing to fear.

00:04:14.820 --> 00:04:18.779
No matter what evil arts
or dark sorcery it is,

00:04:18.780 --> 00:04:20.980
I'll deal with all of it for you.

00:04:26.200 --> 00:04:30.440
(Imperial Preceptor, deal
with Xiao Suisui as soon as possible)

00:04:47.020 --> 00:04:48.659
I'll make them understand

00:04:48.660 --> 00:04:52.980
the price of hurting my son.

00:04:54.060 --> 00:04:56.099
(Hmph, Xiao Heng.)

00:04:56.100 --> 00:04:57.379
(So what if your leg has healed?)

00:04:57.380 --> 00:04:58.779
(In Mother's heart,)

00:04:58.780 --> 00:05:01.420
(I'll always be her favorite son.)

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:27.119
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:30.959
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:34.479
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:34.480 --> 00:05:37.440
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:05:38.320 --> 00:05:41.959
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:05:41.960 --> 00:05:45.720
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:49.119
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:53.160
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:58.760 --> 00:06:02.439
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:06:02.440 --> 00:06:06.079
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:09.799
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:13.439
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:06:13.440 --> 00:06:17.119
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:19.039
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:06:19.040 --> 00:06:25.240
♪Good fortune♪